snippet.title: [Brynn Plays] DELTARUNE Chapter 1 & 2 Longplay (No Commentary)
snippet.description: pacifist main route, plus both secret bosses and as much flavor text, bonus dialogues, and other goodies i could hit. i'm sure i still missed some things but i wanted to make a playthrough as complete as possible for anyone who would rather watch the game than play it. enjoy! :)
